# The Data Intelligence Platform

- **One platform** for data engineering, SQL, streaming, data science & ML — on one governed copy
- **Open lakehouse foundation** — Delta tables on your own cloud storage, in open formats
- **Unified governance** — Unity Catalog over tables, files, models & dashboards, across clouds
- **Data intelligence engine** — generative AI that understands your data: search, auto-optimize
- Formerly the **"Lakehouse Platform"** — renamed for that AI layer
